{"tid":1327540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經過今日先知，原來有咁多老人家都支持暴徒","createTime":"2019-07-17T15:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T16:28:21.000Z","uid":83504,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a3a9fb2884896a9263b23634e0b514911348c83","tid":1327540,"uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:37:49.000Z","msg":"林奠同狗仔一哥有咩回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？仲唔即刻開記招譴責佢地助紂為虐？<br />\n班藍屍廢老見到咁多同齡，甚至仲大過佢地嘅人出嚟聲援班收錢搞事份子，你地又有咩想講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？又話佢地都係收錢？咁多錢收你地做咩唔去埋一份呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺度再一次多謝今日依班咁熱都肯出嚟嘅老人家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好感動<br />\n香港好在仲有你地依班上一輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令我地知道我地做嘅嘢係絕對唔會白費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰班垃圾撐警打人嘅廢老完全冇得同你地比<br />\n你地先係值得我地尊敬，尊重嘅長輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日辛苦你地啦，返到屋企好好咁休息<br />\n我地會繼續努力，絕對唔會辜負你地對我地嘅支持<br />\n<br />\n各位，場仗仲未打完<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地721見</span></span>"},{"pid":"c83cf9b2b5399e49598216b78ded5689253eb706","tid":1327540,"uid":83504,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmAYcn7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmAYcn7.png&h=6712b87c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xwWDWPN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxwWDWPN.png&h=0d6dbe1f&s={SIZE}\" />